2011-11-06  sanderv32@gmail.com

	* Version 1.0 contained a bug. It only checked the password once so that
	  OTP replays where possible. Added the new feature "auth_yubikey_ttl" to cache
	  the password for an amount of time. After the ttl is expired you need to use
	  the Yubikey again to authenticate.

